gigantic negro, stooping a little, presented his flat palm to Flask’s foot, 
and then putting Flask’s hand on his hearse-plumed head and bidding him 
spring as he himself should toss, with one dexterous fling landed the little 
man high and dry on his shoulders. And here was Flask now standing, Daggoo with 
